	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.0-0r.ancient": "徘徊于现实和虚拟的少女，你所求何物？",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.0-0r.next": "回答",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.0-1r.char": "……我在等一个名字被念出来。念到之前，我哪儿都不去。",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.0-1r.next": "继续",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.0-2r.ancient": "你只是害怕“等了却等错”。",

	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.1-0r.ancient": "你又回来。时间对你而言像走廊——你走不完，是因为你不想走完。",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.1-0r.next": "继续",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.1-1r.char": "走廊很好。尽头不好。尽头意味着……不用再等。",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.1-1r.next": "继续",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.1-2r.ancient": "愚蠢。你若不走向尽头，就永远只是回声。",

	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.2-0r.ancient": "那就站着吧。塔会替你记住：你来过，很多次，却什么也没拿走。",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.2-0r.next": "继续",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.2-1r.char": "拿走什么....",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.2-1r.next": "继续",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-SAKAYORI_IROHA.2-2r.ancient": "你要是真的想拯救那个少女，就不应该止步于此。",
