	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "我是从月亮来的辉夜～顺着七色光柱跳来这里，正忙着找彩叶呢。",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "月球来客，却为凡人执念踏足高塔，不守规矩。",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.0-1.next": "回答",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.0-2.char": "是彩叶的歌声引我来的！遇见她我才懂心意，我一定要找到她。",

	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.1-0r.char": "我回来啦！这里虽怪却有趣，但我还是要去找彩叶，别拦我。",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.1-0r.next": "继续",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.1-1r.ancient": "为虚妄牵绊穿梭时空，不过是自寻迷途。",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.1-1r.next": "反驳",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.1-2r.char": "才不是迷途！彩叶是我最重要的人，为她穿梭多少次都值得。",

	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.2-0r.char": "我懂你守着秩序，不想惹麻烦……但别拦我见彩叶。",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.2-0r.next": "继续",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.2-1r.ancient": "外来者无权违背高塔法则，你的执念终将让你消散。",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.2-1r.next": "宣战",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.2-2r.char": "我不会消散！手环里的歌声指引我回来，谁也拦不住我。",

	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.3-0r.ancient": "[jitter]呵啊！[/jitter]\n[jitter][red]被情感困住的月之残响，可笑至极，就此消散！[/red][/jitter]",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.3-0r.next": "继续",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.3-1r.ancient": "凭任性违抗宿命与秩序，太过天真！[jitter][/jitter]",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.3-1r.next": "继续",
	"THE_ARCHITECT.talk.KAGUYA-HINA_CHARACTER.3-2r.char": "这不是天真！彩叶的歌声就是我的力量，我要打破秩序回到她身边！"
